msgid ""
"Next, &kmymoney; imports the data and creates all necessary objects, such as "
"payee information, account and category records, and stock price "
"information. Wherever possible, existing transactions will be matched "
"against the imported information, to avoid duplicate transactions. A "
"progress bar is shown and updated during the import process."
msgstr ""
"Zatim, &kappname; unosi podatke i kreira sve potrebne objekte, kao što su "
"informacije o osobi koja vrši transakcije, računi i zapisi kategorija i "
"informacije o cijenama dionica. Gdjegod je to moguće, postojeće transakcije "
"će se povezati sa unesenim informacijama. \n"
"Bar koji označava dokle je proces došao će biti prikazan i mijenjaće se kako "
"proces bude odmicao."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:587
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In case &kappname; could not detect the name of the account to be "
#| "imported, the user will be asked to select the account into which the "
#| "data should be imported. If the account does not already exist in your "
#| "file, a new account can be created by clicking on <guibutton>Create</"
#| "guibutton>."
msgid ""
"In case &kmymoney; could not detect the name of the account to be imported, "
"the user will be asked to select the account into which the data should be "
"imported. If the account does not already exist in your file, a new account "
"can be created by clicking <guibutton>Create</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"U slučaju da &kappname; ne može prepoznati ime računa koji se unosi, "
"korisnik će morati odabrati račun u koji se podaci unose. Ukoliko račun ne "
"postoji, novi račun će biti kreiran klikom na <guibutton>Create</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp.docbook:594
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "At the end of the import, &kappname; shows a statement import statistics "
